US Descr Str: The Little Jack's main cannon. It's rather old,\nbut Drachma has kept it in great shape.
The main cannon used on Valuan Warships,\nsometimes available on the Black Market.
An upgraded version of the Standard Valuan\nCannon, used on light warships in Mid Ocean.
Cannons used on Armada ships, when they defeated\nIxa'taka. Slightly outdated, but powerful.
An upgraded version of the G-Type Cannon, with\nthe same basic design, but greater firepower.
A rotating cannon that can track enemy targets,\nbut doesn't do much damage.
A new rotating main cannon developed for Valuan\nDestroyers. Available on the Black Market.
A large and powerful cannon based on traditional\nYafutoman craftmanship.
A durable cannon made from ancient metals from\nthe Old World.
A very large cannon that enables large ships to \nblast small ships out of the sky.
A small caliber secondary cannon for smaller \nships.
A secondary cannon for the Little Jack. An\nupgraded version of the 3 Inch Cannon.
A secondary cannon for the Little Jack. More\npowerful than the 3 Inch Cannon.
A secondary cannon for the Little Jack.\nA modified version of the Main Cannon.
A high-caliber secondary cannon developed for\nwarships.
The first 10 Inch secondary cannon, developed\nby the Nasrean Navy.
A 10 inch secondary cannon with a reinforced\nbarrel that helps to absorb shock.
A high-caliber secondary cannon, only used\non larger ships.
A secondary cannon developed in Yafutoma,\ninspired by cylindrical plants.
A secondary cannon used by the Yafutoman Navy.\nIt is a short-range, high-powered cannon.
A light torpedo, well-suited for smaller ships.\nAfter launch, it attacks its target from above.
A torpedo equippable by the Little Jack. Has the\nhighest chance to hit out of all the torpedos.
A torpedo equippable by the Little Jack.\nAfter launch, it charges its target from above.
A torpedo equippable by the Little Jack. Has\ngreater range than standard torpedos.

The Little Jack's ultimate weapon. It was\nacquired to destroy Rhaknam.
The ultimate weapon of the Delphinus. Builds up\nMoon energy and releases it in a massive blast.

A rotating cannon designed for battleships.\nHas Red properties, and high accuracy.
A secondary cannon designed for battleships.\nHas Blue properties, and high accuracy.

Made of a special alloy for added durability.\nHas Purple properties, and great firepower.
